text:
KEYS
Seriously, man. I'm just being honest,

I think the bunny suit
is just a little much.

MOUSER
Excuse me?

KEYS
Right... Rabbit. Okay, my fault.

MOUSER
Hey, 40-year-old virgin! Get over here!

KEYS
Let's go.

MOUSER
Uh-huh, Captain Khakis, come here.

- Let's go, let's go.
- Come on, bud!

KEYS
Closer.

MOUSER
There he is. Blue Shirt Guy.

GUY
Blue shirt!
Yes!
Hello, officer.
Rabbit?

MOUSER
Nice skin!

GUY
Thank you! How sweet.

MOUSER
How'd you get it?

GUY
Well, uh, mostly genetics, I think,

I'm pretty lucky,
I have naturally dewy skin.

KEYS
Listen up, Neutrogena.

You know you can't go around
looking like that. The rules are clear.

And another thing: you can't
hack the NPC avatars!

- No sir!
- It screws up the mission log...

- Screws it up!
- ...and makes the game look bad.

MOUSER
Horrible!

KEYS
[Spits]

GUY
I got like, 5% of that.

MOUSER
Lose the skin!

GUY
I... Lose... How am I supposed to
get rid of my skin?

MOUSER
Take it off, man!

Just take it off,
what are you doing?

- What?
- Seriously.

- The whole thing, the face, the outfit.
- How?

MOUSER
Everything. Ditch it.

If you don't,
we're gonna kill you.

- Why?
- And we're gonna keep killing you.

GUY
Still why?

MOUSER
Until we do find out who you are,

and then we're
gonna ban you for life!

GUY
Okay, no-no, okay, I-I want to comply!

I just find the order of
those threats very confusing!

- Somebody's about to get shot!
- Light him up!
